1
00:00:23,030 --> 00:00:24,100
Thank you

2
00:00:24,488 --> 00:00:26,857
This was my happiest night in Teyvat

3
00:00:28,116 --> 00:00:29,717
Farewell, Columbina

4
00:01:09,475 --> 00:01:10,425
The moon

5
00:01:10,700 --> 00:01:13,834
Really is closer than ever tonight...

6
00:01:22,826 --> 00:01:23,600
...Columbina!

7
00:01:25,925 --> 00:01:28,434
All three moons in one place...

8
00:01:28,927 --> 00:01:31,331
Time for one final experiment

9
00:01:31,825 --> 00:01:35,850
Reason, life, death, time, and space...

10
00:01:36,330 --> 00:01:38,800
They all believed I would fail...

11
00:01:45,859 --> 00:01:46,931
How could this happen!?

12
00:01:49,403 --> 00:01:51,437
But Teyvat's primordial power

13
00:01:51,437 --> 00:01:53,864
Never did belong to the throne of heaven

14
00:01:55,815 --> 00:01:56,890
And now

15
00:01:57,970 --> 00:01:59,132
They are mine

16
00:02:27,953 --> 00:02:28,682
(No...)

17
00:02:28,682 --> 00:02:30,135
(As long as I'm here...)

18
00:02:31,117 --> 00:02:34,066
(The Doctor is free to wield the three moons' power...)

19
00:02:40,394 --> 00:02:41,567
(It's the only way...)

20
00:02:49,207 --> 00:02:50,118
I guess

21
00:02:50,620 --> 00:02:52,710
I won't be going home today...

22
00:02:53,586 --> 00:02:54,444
Columbina

23
00:02:56,334 --> 00:02:56,959
No!

24
00:03:26,629 --> 00:03:30,421
Stubborn world... Do not try to control me...!

25
00:03:38,170 --> 00:03:39,637
Columbina...

